            <title>Version 0.9.0</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 22:21:11 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
<li>Beta Updates — opt into early access builds via Settings > Lab</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Sessions now disappear immediately when the agent exits</li>
<li>Improved session detection reliability</li>
<li>Fixed hover highlight on session rows</li>
</ul>]]></description>
