        <item>
            <title>Version 0.6.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 01:44:25 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Smart suppression</b> — notifications don't auto-expand when you're looking at the agent's terminal tab. Detects the focused pane in iTerm, Terminal.app, Ghostty, and WezTerm/Kaku. Falls back to app-level detection for Warp and cmux. Enabled by default in Settings > Behavior.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Session metadata occasionally cleared during discovery snapshots</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/bluedusk/xisland/releases/download/v0.6.0/XIsland.zip"
                sparkle:version="884"
