        <item>
            <title>Version 0.4.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 21:01:04 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
<li>See code changes directly in permission request cards</li>
<li>Deny button on permission requests</li>
<li>"Always Allow" option for trusted edits</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Terminal losing focus while xIsland is running</li>
<li>Keyboard navigation responding slowly when opening the overlay</li>
</ul>
<h3>Improved</h3>
<ul>
<li>Cleaner menu bar — no extra icon in release builds</li>
<li>Faster session discovery and smoother UI updates</li>
</ul>]]></description>
